text: Kerstin Ahlqvist (11 July 1927 - 2 October 2000) was a Swedish alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1952 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2000 deaths Category:Swedish female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Sweden Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:People from Frösön
